    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the ragù is thickening, add your<strong> gnocchi</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>gnocchi</strong> for 3 min or until it begins to rise to the top of the pot</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked gnocchi</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 5,
