    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>hearty mushroom, basil & lentil gnocchi ragù </strong>to<strong> </strong>an<strong> oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over your<strong> grated</strong> <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 10-15 min or until bubbling and golden – this is your <strong>hearty mushroom, basil & lentil gnocchi ragù bake</strong></p>",
