      "instruction": "<p>Once done, remove the dish from the oven and leave to stand for 5 min before serving (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Serve the <strong>hearty mushroom, basil & lentil ragù gnocchi bake</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
